skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: car ratings
des: Looking for a used car online? Ask Car Ratings during your search to find the vehicle rating from www.carcomplaints.com for most years, makes and models. Can be used as a tool when searching for used cars online, just ask Alexa to search Car Ratings for the year, make and model.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
